---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Waitlist" current="Waitlist" description="Pre-launch waitlist for MPower. Knowledge. Power. Yours.">

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container narrow">
      <div class="mono kicker">§ Pre-launch · 2026</div>
      <h1 class="display wl-h1">
        Take what's <span class="i-accent">yours.</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="body-lg wl-lede">
        MPower opens in stages. MPower Agri and MPower Ed launch first; MPower Teams is here now, by arrangement. Tell us who you are and we'll let you in when your community is ready.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-tight">
    <div class="container narrow">
      {/* Klaviyo embedded form. Powered by the onsite script + init in
          Base.astro (company SKABCW). The form fields, validation, success
          state and double opt-in are all managed in Klaviyo - this div is
          the mount point. Per the 18 May 2026 spec. */}
      <div class="klaviyo-form-W2JdnP"></div>

      <noscript>
        <p class="body wl-fallback">
          The waitlist form needs JavaScript. If it isn't loading, email
          <a href="mailto:hello@mpowerhq.nz">hello@mpowerhq.nz</a> and we'll add you by hand.
        </p>
      </noscript>

      <p class="body-sm wl-promise">
        We won't sell your address. We won't spam. We'll write maybe once a month, and only when there's something real to say. Nobody is ever selling you anything in here, including us.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

</Base>

<style>
  .narrow { max-width: 920px; }
  .kicker { color: var(--c-spring); margin-bottom: 32px; }
  .wl-h1 { font-size: var(--t-h1); line-height: 1.04; padding-bottom: 0.12em; }
  .wl-lede { margin-top: 48px; max-width: 60ch; opacity: .9; }

  .klaviyo-form-W2JdnP { margin-top: 8px; min-height: 120px; }

  .wl-fallback { margin-top: 24px; opacity: .9; }
  .wl-fallback a { color: var(--c-spring); }

  .wl-promise {
    margin-top: 36px;
    padding-top: 24px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--c-rule);
    max-width: 560px;
    font-style: italic;
    opacity: .85;
  }
</style>
